&lt;li&gt;Manage the environmental permits and certification requirements as well as processing material/vendor management for the proper storage and disposal of chemicals and waste.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as point of contact with regulatory agencies for permitting, audits, for emergency preparedness/response.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
